Prisoner. Q.Whether there was not another person in the room at the time I was looking at the bonnet? - A. Yes;
Lucy Patrick
, the shop-woman.

Mr. Gurney. (To
Ann Hornsby
). Q. Look at these spoons? - A. I know this spoon that was bent very well, it is Mr. Oldham's; I know it by the marks in the bowl.

Q. How do you know he took him that night? - A. I was in the house when he was taken;
Sarah Lettin
, is my sister, and I was there to see her.
